            "title": "Implementing CADR Requirements for NIH Websites: A Case Study",
            "id": "c9727a09-dc79-403b-bf3f-5e368ee8f66d",
            "description": "Today, on April 6, 2026, Information Management Services, Inc. (IMS) unveiled its latest white paper titled \"Implementing CADR Requirements for NIH Websites: A Case Study.\" This publication serves as a guide for organizations to adhere to the National Institutes of Health (NIH) standards, focusing on Comprehensive Accessible Data Repository (CADR) implementation. The white paper offers a strategic framework to aid in compliance, aiming to assist organizations in meeting the requirements set by the NIH.",
